{"article_id":"EpS6SCmvaSr4OExU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The police shooting of a man in Charlotte , N.C. , sparked overnight protests and unrest .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Protesters threw rocks at police ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"injuring 16 officers ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"while police","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"wearing riot gear","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"fired tear gas into the crowds .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"At one point , a major interstate was shut down","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"as protesters set a fire","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and vandalized police cars .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The protests began Tuesday night","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"after police shot and killed 43-year-old Keith Lamont Scott at an apartment complex near the University of North Carolina , Charlotte .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Officers were at the complex","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to serve a warrant for a different man ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The Associated Press reports ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"when they saw Scott in a car .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Police and protesters give different accounts of what happened next .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Police say","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"he came out of the vehicle with a gun .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"At a press conference on Wednesday , Charlotte-Mecklenburg police Chief Kerr Putney said","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that officers gave the man multiple verbal warnings","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to drop his weapon","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"before he was shot .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Putney says","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"a handgun was recovered on the scene ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and that witnesses corroborated the officer 's accounts .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Around the Nation","depth":2},{"id":26,"text":"Family Disputes Claims","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Man","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Who Police Killed","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Was Armed","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Family Disputes Claims","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Man","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Who Police Killed","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Was Armed","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Listen · 3:03","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"3:03","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"The police chief says","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"he does not know","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"if Scott pointed the weapon at the officers ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"or whether the gun was loaded .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"He also says","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"the officer","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"who shot Scott","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"was not wearing a bodycam ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"but that other video footage of the incident is being reviewed .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Scott 's family , and the protesters","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"who gathered last night ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"tell a different story ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"reports Gwendolyn Glenn of member station WFAE .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"`` The daughter of Keith Lamont Scott says","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that her father did not have a gun ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"that he was not armed ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"and that he was sitting in the car","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"reading a book","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"waiting on his son to get off a bus from school , ''","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"she says .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Officer Brentley Vinson shot Scott ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"who later died in the hospital ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"the AP reports .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Vinson ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"who has been with the department for two years ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"is on administrative leave","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"while police investigate the shooting","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"- standard department procedure ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"the wire service says .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"After the shooting , the woman","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"who says","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"she is Scott 's daughter","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"streamed live on Facebook for an hour ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"as Nick de la Canal of member station WFAE reports .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"She cursed at officers at the scene ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"her father was disabled","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and did n't have a gun .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"`` Y'all m * * * * * * * * * * * s running for him","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"because he 's black , ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"The video went viral","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and protesters began to gather at the area ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"de la Canal says .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Glenn was n't present for the start of the protest","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"but says","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"according to witnesses ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"it began peacefully .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"De la Canal has this account of what happened next :","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"`` [ A ] s the night wore on ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"more protesters arrived ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"and the mood turned more aggressive .","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"They forced the shutdown of Old Concord Road , right next to the rail tracks .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"`` Overhead , a police helicopter was swinging its search light over the crowd ,","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"which stretched all the way down the street .","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"``","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"Just as the 11 o'clock freight train passed ,","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"protesters began throwing rocks and water bottles at police ,","depth":16},{"id":95,"text":"and smashing in the windows of police cruisers ,","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"some so badly","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"they had to be towed from the scene .","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"Then , at once , police in riot gear , donned gas masks and helmets ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"and began shooting rounds of tear gas into the crowd . ''","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"De la Canal reports","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that protesters wrapped T-shirts around their faces ;","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"some knelt","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"and raised their arms","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"as they faced off with the officers .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"He continues :","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"`` As police fired more rounds of tear gas ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"protesters began grabbing the canisters","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"and throwing them back .","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"And a new wave of rocks and bricks were hurled at the officers ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"and a cloud of gas rose over the intersection ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"glowing green in the light of the traffic signal . ``","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"By midnight , the protesters had moved on .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"They set off down the ramp to W.T . Harris Blvd. ,","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"where they stopped traffic","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"and smashed another police cruiser .","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"They banged on the hood of the car in time to chants of 'no justice , no peace . ' `` And over the course of the night , they moved to I-85","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"and blocked traffic there","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"and started a bonfire in the middle of the highway . ''","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"In the early hours of Wednesday , a stretch of the interstate was closed in both directions","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"because of the protests ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"but it had reopened by rush hour .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"At the press conference Wednesday , the police chief said","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"about 16 officers were injured over the course of the night , none of them seriously .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"One person was arrested","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"as a result of the protests ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Putney said .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"The Associated Press says","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"that one TV news crew withdrew from covering the protests","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"`` after demonstrators began rocking their remote van . '' The mayor of Charlotte , Jennifer Roberts , `` appealed for calm","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"and tweeted","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"that 'the community deserves answers , ' ``","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"the AP says .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"By Wednesday morning ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"the wire service reports ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"the streets were quiet - broken glass and rocks the only evidence of the night 's unrest .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"U.S. Attorney General Loretta Lynch said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"that the Justice Department is assessing the incident","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"and is in regular contact with local authorities .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"`` I urge those","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"demonstrating in Charlotte","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"to remain peaceful in their expressions of protest and concern , ''","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"Glenn tells NPR","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"there was tension recently in Charlotte over a 2013 police shooting of a black man , Jonathan Ferrell .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Ferrell was unarmed","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"when he was killed by a white officer ;","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"the case went to trial last year .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"`` That trial ended in a hung jury","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"and","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"when that verdict came down","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"there were protests in the streets immediately , ''","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"Glenn says .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"`` Police and the protesters did not clash at that time ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"but the city was greatly divided . ''","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Tuesday night 's shooting and protests in North Carolina come just days after a police officer in Tulsa , Okla. , shot and killed an unarmed black man .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"That shooting happened Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"and video was released on Monday .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"Tulsa Police Chief Chuck Jordan said","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"the video ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"which shows Terence Crutcher walking to his car with his hands over his head","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"before the officer shot him ,","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"was `` very disturbing . ''","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"The killing is being investigated by police and by the Justice Department .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":327,"left":188,"right":326,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":172,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":0,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":168,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":165,"right":167,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":166,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":6,"right":169,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":177,"right":186,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":173,"right":176,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":9,"right":1